    "Relevant information pertaining to the user's question is delivered to the large language model, which then integrates this information to generate a response.",
    "Process diagram of knowledge graph construction method.",
    "The construction process of the pattern layer is based on the national standards of Traditional Chinese Medicine and the specific structure of medical cases, which encompasses the definition of entity types and relationship types.",
    "The data extraction process involves selecting appropriate medical cases from the Medical Cases of Wang Zhongqi, followed by automated entity recognition using a large-scale language model.",
    "Subsequently, knowledge fusion is conducted individually for different entity types, resulting in the formation of relationship triples."
